      passage: `<p>To coders like the software engineer Priya Sundaram, the programming languages Rust and Lua differ plainly: the first enforces strict memory safety and the second does not. Yet because grasping either language calls for deeply technical know-how, people outside the field _____ to tell the two apart.</p>`,
