      passage: `<p>Like a great deal of scientific research, a well-known 2019 study of desert ants in <em>Current Biology</em> grew out of the pooled labor and know-how of several _____ Pauline Fleischmann appears first in the byline, but Robin Grob, Wolfgang Rössler, and further coauthors contributed a great deal as well.</p>`,
